      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so u mentioned proponents think it'll spur investment, but some of the recent studies i'm seeing say that the trickle-down effect hasn't really worked in the past. do the current projections actually support the idea that this will help the middle class, or is it mostly just going to stay at the top?",
